@MartinHlavna you may mark folders with generated files as 'excluded' (right-click on it in the Project View). However, you may lose some functionality for these files.

Another option is to pause indexing. The button is to the right from the progress bar. Don't forget to resume later.

But 'few minutes' sounds like quite a while. How many files are generated? How many lines of code in total (or what's the total size in kB)?
